Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.24,0:00:08.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Christmas is just\Naround the corner, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.70,0:00:10.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you guys already have plans?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.62,0:00:12.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not doing anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.33,0:00:14.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Master Raku...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.92,0:00:18.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My father won't be home\Non Christmas Eve, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.67,0:00:20.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be home...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.01,0:00:22.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, I mean, of course I'll be\Nspending it with Honey!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.68,0:00:24.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My, how callous!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.43,0:00:27.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, since we are here, why don't\Nwe throw a Christmas party?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.60,0:00:29.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You know, get together\Nand have a blast?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.68,0:00:32.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, as long as the event\Nplanner's a no-show.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.44,0:00:34.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even though it was my idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.73,0:00:36.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So? What are we gonna do for real?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.94,0:00:39.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In our case, we really do have to...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.98,0:00:43.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ch-Christmas?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.61,0:00:44.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chitoge?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.79,0:02:22.80,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"Need"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.72,0:02:29.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your mom's coming back?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.51,0:02:30.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.68,0:02:34.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Every Christmas, my mom comes home,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.31,0:02:36.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and it's just the three of\Nus over the holidays,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.56,0:02:39.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so it doesn't look like\NI can attend that party.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.35,0:02:41.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why does that\Nmake you hate Christmas?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.23,0:02:47.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it,\Nwhere is your mom usually?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.99,0:02:50.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, she doesn't\Nseem to be living with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.28,0:02:52.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She's traveling all over the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.87,0:02:56.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She's still working as\Na high-powered female CEO.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.12,0:02:57.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That mom of mine...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.54,0:02:58.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...is incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.08,0:03:00.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She owns companies all over the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.88,0:03:04.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and I've heard that her annual\Nincome once topped 10 billion dollars!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.55,0:03:07.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Her schedule's crammed\Nfor the next ten years,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.17,0:03:09.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and it's even been said
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.59,0:03:13.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,that the Nikkei Index fluctuates\Naccording to my mom's mood that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.64,0:03:16.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She seriously sounds\Nlike a total badass.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.68,0:03:19.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But most incredible of all...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.56,0:03:21.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She's scary when she gets mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.86,0:03:23.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Absolutely terrifying!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.82,0:03:25.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That scary? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.15,0:03:30.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But she sounds like a good mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.53,0:03:35.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Spending Christmas with you\Nevery year when she's so busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.20,0:03:37.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is she... really?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.71,0:03:41.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a little uncomfortable with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.21,0:03:45.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mom had me when\Nshe was really young,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.21,0:03:48.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but she's been wrapped up\Nin her work ever since,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.13,0:03:52.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so as far back as I can remember,\NI've only seen her a few times a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.68,0:03:57.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, I don't really know\Nhow it feels to have a mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.14,0:04:04.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why should I have to\Ntell you all this stuff?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.07,0:04:06.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who brought it up...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.78,0:04:10.03,DefaultMid2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dad
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.78,0:04:10.03,DefaultTop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Incoming call
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.07,0:04:08.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? It's from Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.99,0:04:10.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What does he want?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.70,0:04:11.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whaaat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.37,0:04:15.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.08,0:04:19.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He says Mom's\Ncoming home tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.12,0:04:21.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What? But it's not even Christmas yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.58,0:04:25.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And also...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.84,0:04:28.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He wants to introduce you to my mom,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.21,0:04:30.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so he told me to invite you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.14,0:04:37.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Where the hell's\Nthat wine I ordered?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.72,0:04:39.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How's the decorating going?\NIs the food ready yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.97,0:04:41.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're doing it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.39,0:04:43.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.65,0:04:46.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They're unusually nimble today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.11,0:04:48.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like they're on high alert.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.32,0:04:49.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry the hell up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.40,0:04:52.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Madam Flower will be arriving soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.57,0:04:54.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Madam Flower?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.53,0:04:56.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They're talking about my mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.28,0:04:59.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Since Mom's first name is Hana Kirisaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.45,0:05:04.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see you came dressed\Nin a suit, like I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.71,0:05:07.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do we really need to go this far?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.13,0:05:09.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's just your mom coming home, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.55,0:05:10.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be such an idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.88,0:05:11.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Look, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.72,0:05:14.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,try saying or doing something\Nfunny in front of Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.68,0:05:16.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You won't live to tell the tale!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.14,0:05:17.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How scary can she be?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.97,0:05:19.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Be on your best behavior, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.85,0:05:22.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm introducing you to her\Nas my boyfriend, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.77,0:05:23.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.60,0:05:28.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Still, no matter how\Ndressed up you get,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.61,0:05:31.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,you wear that ribbon\Nno matter what, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.11,0:05:36.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't change ribbons like\Nyou did the other day, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.24,0:05:39.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, sure, I have\Nother ribbons, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.41,0:05:42.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But this ribbon is special.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.50,0:05:45.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because Mom gave it to me years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.21,0:05:49.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Raku! Long time no see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.71,0:05:51.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.21,0:05:53.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to summon you on short notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.67,0:05:55.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Have you been doing okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.13,0:05:56.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.05,0:05:59.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's just been so hard, finding\Ntime to introduce you to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.80,0:06:01.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're welcome here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.18,0:06:02.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.10,0:06:06.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Daddy has\Na stomachache all of a sudden!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.44,0:06:08.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Would you mind\Ntaking over from here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.23,0:06:09.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can't do that to me, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.65,0:06:11.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You stay right here with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.40,0:06:13.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How freaked out are you two?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.86,0:06:16.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Madam Flower has arrived!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.79,0:06:28.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She is here for real, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.42,0:06:30.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Take your positions, everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.09,0:06:40.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.76,0:06:43.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home, Madam!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.19,0:06:52.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So this is Chitoge's mom?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.57,0:06:54.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's a real beauty!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.57,0:06:57.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I mean, she's got this amazing aura.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.66,0:07:01.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But... even if she had\NChitoge at a young age...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.45,0:07:04.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...come on, she can't be this young!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.24,0:07:06.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If she told me she was her\Nbig sister, I'd believe her!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.16,0:07:08.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Hana...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.92,0:07:11.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a long time!\NI've missed you so!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.96,0:07:14.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home, my beloved wife!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.21,0:07:17.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Adelt!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.76,0:07:19.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home, Adelt!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.43,0:07:21.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've missed you, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.76,0:07:23.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You must be worn out\Nfrom all that hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.81,0:07:26.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I think you've lost some\Nweight, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.02,0:07:28.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How long can you stay in Japan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.85,0:07:31.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be here till Christmas night.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.40,0:07:35.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Although I'll only have 2 hours\Nand 36 minutes for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.28,0:07:38.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.07,0:07:40.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She actually looks pretty nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.36,0:07:42.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Though you weren't joking\Nabout her crazy schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.63,0:07:45.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Can you take a short break, maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.12,0:07:47.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For today, we've prepared\Nall of your favorites.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.58,0:07:50.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but it's right back\Nto work for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.37,0:07:52.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Adelt...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.08,0:07:54.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.46,0:07:59.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Two months and 15 days ago, I asked you\Nto do something for me, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.84,0:08:03.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Since you said you knew one of\Nthe directors of that brokerage in Rome,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.55,0:08:07.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I asked you to arrange\Nfor a deal with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.64,0:08:09.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever became of that, I wonder?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.93,0:08:13.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, Hana, the thing is,\Nit's pretty complicated, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.52,0:08:16.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm asking you a question, Adelt.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.90,0:08:18.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Did you get it done?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.23,0:08:19.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.49,0:08:20.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Which is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.99,0:08:22.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't done a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.82,0:08:26.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lock him up in the library right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.03,0:08:30.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't get it done by Christmas,\NI'm going to gouge your eyeballs!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.37,0:08:33.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}T-Terrifying!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.79,0:08:36.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I mean, that is a gang\Nboss she's talking to!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.17,0:08:39.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jeez, the old guy's a total\Nhenpecked husband!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.21,0:08:41.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then... Is Chitoge around?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.34,0:08:42.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.39,0:08:46.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Long time no see!\NHave you been well?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.26,0:08:47.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.64,0:08:49.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,how old are you now, again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.93,0:08:51.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.43,0:08:53.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I am now sixteen years old! Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.44,0:08:54.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Mother"?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.77,0:08:57.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see. You've grown up a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.44,0:08:58.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What about school?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.98,0:09:00.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.49,0:09:04.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I was ranked fifth in our grade\Nafter a test the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.95,0:09:06.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see... fifth?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.37,0:09:08.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chitoge?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.16,0:09:11.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That really doesn't\Nmake sense, does it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.12,0:09:15.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That junior high you graduated from was\None of the top schools in the U.S.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.42,0:09:18.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And you graduated first in your class.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.04,0:09:20.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As for the high school\Nyou're attending now,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.05,0:09:24.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I hear that it's quite average by\NJapanese academic standards.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.01,0:09:25.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So what's wrong with this picture?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.59,0:09:27.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I promise to study harder!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.10,0:09:32.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Chitoge's so freaked out,\Nshe's vibrating like a cell phone!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.52,0:09:35.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But still, this mom of hers is deadly scary.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.10,0:09:37.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The intimidation factor is mind-blowing!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.02,0:09:38.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.36,0:09:41.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who on earth is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.78,0:09:45.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mother! Allow me to introduce him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.99,0:09:48.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is my boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.45,0:09:49.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,P-Pleased to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.91,0:09:51.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Raku Ichijo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.50,0:09:53.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.33,0:09:55.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ichijo?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.87,0:09:57.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ichijo, as in... surely not...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.17,0:10:00.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. It's probably what\Nyou're thinking of...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.67,0:10:02.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ichijo as in the Shuei-gumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.63,0:10:04.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but I assure you,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.01,0:10:08.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm seeing your daughter in the most\Nimpeccable, honorable way imaginable.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.26,0:10:09.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.64,0:10:12.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please look after my\Ndaughter, little boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.14,0:10:13.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.27,0:10:18.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you ever hurt her in any way,\Nwhat I'm going to do to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.52,0:10:19.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Can you imagine it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.32,0:10:22.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.69,0:10:24.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rest assured!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.99,0:10:27.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because I'll exceed anything\Nyou might imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.91,0:10:30.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's scaring me at\Nevery turn, this woman!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.37,0:10:34.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Still, a boyfriend for you, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.00,0:10:35.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My, how time flies!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.37,0:10:37.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So you've reached that age, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.21,0:10:42.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's this...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.46,0:10:44.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That ribbon...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.38,0:10:47.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're still wearing that thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.84,0:10:49.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's completely frayed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.72,0:10:53.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A ribbon like that, I can\Nbuy you as many as you need.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.85,0:10:55.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're a girl, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.31,0:10:59.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You need to be more stylish, or\Nyou'll chase your boyfriend away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.27,0:11:01.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wear a prettier one, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.77,0:11:03.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.36,0:11:06.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then, that's it for me today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.28,0:11:08.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chitoge?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.32,0:11:11.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have a nice chat\Non Christmas Eve, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.74,0:11:15.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have to admit, she really was a terror.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.62,0:11:17.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Like a storm.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.79,0:11:19.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Madam, we have a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.67,0:11:21.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Another secretary has collapsed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.58,0:11:24.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Again? How many does\Nthat make this month?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.67,0:11:28.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I swear, it's a mere\N72-hour shift... how pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.13,0:11:29.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Any backups?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.43,0:11:33.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, all of them are\Nstill in the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.18,0:11:35.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is that right? That is a problem, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.68,0:11:36.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.02,0:11:38.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, little boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.40,0:11:45.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Starting now, till Christmas,\Nwork as my secretary.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.94,0:11:49.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.49,0:11:51.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mother, are you serious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.41,0:11:53.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My, my! Of course I'm serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.99,0:11:57.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have no intention of allowing\Nmy daughter to date a do-nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.50,0:11:59.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The timing couldn't be better,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.29,0:12:04.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and I'm thinking it will give me the chance\Nto see for myself if he's worthy of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.84,0:12:06.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, but that doesn't mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.42,0:12:08.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But seriously...\Nyour secretary, all of a—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.80,0:12:11.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you're not up to it, then\Nthat's fine with me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.55,0:12:15.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I'll have you\Ndrowned in Tokyo Bay tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.77,0:12:17.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That said...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.39,0:12:22.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you do manage to gain my approval,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.73,0:12:29.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll reward you two with a night in an\Nultra suite at a five-star hotel on Christmas Eve.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.28,0:12:32.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.03,0:12:34.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Carry him to the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.57,0:12:35.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.45,0:12:37.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm seriously doing this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.37,0:12:39.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ichijo... right.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.08,0:12:43.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That kid from ten years ago, eh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.58,0:12:46.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now, then, let's see\Nhow you've grown.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.17,0:12:53.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well! You do clean up nicely.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.34,0:12:55.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... am I really gonna do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.80,0:12:57.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's so out of the blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.43,0:12:58.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.89,0:13:00.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.27,0:13:04.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All you have to do is follow\Nmy every order, to the letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.31,0:13:07.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For starters, skim through these.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.48,0:13:08.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's my schedule for today,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.94,0:13:12.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and also a manual for what's\Nexpected of you as my secretary.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.78,0:13:13.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.78,0:13:15.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Memorize it all in five minutes, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.87,0:13:18.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.54,0:13:20.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Put together your proposals
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.12,0:13:23.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,on how the 5 EU corporations should\Nmake inroads into new markets.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.67,0:13:25.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What did the research yield?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.67,0:13:28.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Unbelievable... Look at\Nall these documents!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.13,0:13:30.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is this really just her\Nschedule for today?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.67,0:13:33.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've never seen a minute-by-minute\Nschedule before in my life!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.43,0:13:35.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Not only that... though\NI can't be sure about this...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.84,0:13:37.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That meeting she's\Nbeen taking part in.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.97,0:13:41.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As far as I can tell, she's speaking in\Nat least five different languages!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.22,0:13:44.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What kind of a high-spec\Nmom is she, anyway?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.35,0:13:45.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.65,0:13:48.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's first on the agenda\Ntoday, little boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.98,0:13:50.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.15,0:13:52.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Today, you're going to head over to...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.90,0:13:54.24,DefaultBot,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,RAKU
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.40,0:13:55.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This company's gigantic!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.07,0:13:58.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?\NGet yourself over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.49,0:14:04.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I am sincerely sorry for summoning you\Nhere on account of our blunder.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.83,0:14:07.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please step on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.13,0:14:08.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not happening! That's revolting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.71,0:14:11.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The president of a major\Ncorporation is prostrating himself!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.34,0:14:14.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Putting me to so much trouble\Nwhen it was your own mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.76,0:14:16.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You certainly have some nerve.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.64,0:14:19.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please accept my sincere...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.05,0:14:20.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She stepped on him anyway!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.35,0:14:22.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just what kind of a hotshot is she?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.97,0:14:24.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.77,0:14:25.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.73,0:14:26.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.77,0:14:31.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's still too early\Nfor you to call me "Mother."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.78,0:14:33.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then what should I call you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.82,0:14:34.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.74,0:14:38.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As a special privilege, I'm going to\Nlet you call me "Ms. Hana."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.07,0:14:40.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Then Ms. Hana...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.08,0:14:41.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What am I supposed to do, exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.95,0:14:43.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.29,0:14:45.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, your first task, little boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.62,0:14:48.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go buy a Coke\Nsomewhere around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.92,0:14:50.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Within the next three hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.13,0:14:53.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A Coke, did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.01,0:14:54.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.88,0:14:57.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If there's anything else I need,\NI'll let you know later.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.39,0:15:02.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This might actually be an easy job.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.22,0:15:08.40,DefaultTop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hana Kirisaki\NConnected
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.64,0:15:05.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hello? It's me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.52,0:15:08.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's something I'd like to add\Nto your shopping list. Do you mind?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.85,0:15:09.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Hana?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.73,0:15:11.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. What should I get?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.40,0:15:13.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You see, the daughter of\None of my clients in Canada{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.82,0:15:18.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}is absolutely pining for a stuffed animal\Nthat's only available at Disney*** in Japan,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.61,0:15:20.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}so could you go get one?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.87,0:15:26.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Also, I want you to buy the entire line of Japan-only\Nlimited editions of Chan** handbags. Also...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.33,0:15:27.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hold up! Hold up a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.21,0:15:28.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dis***?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.29,0:15:31.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, but do you know\Nhow long it'll take to travel?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.17,0:15:32.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, but that's not my concern.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.67,0:15:34.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Figure it out somehow.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.09,0:15:36.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You can charge as much\Nas you need on my card.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.17,0:15:37.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just make sure you do your best.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.88,0:15:39.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Figure it out, did she say?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.13,0:15:41.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And let me remind you,\NI expect you to be punctual.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.43,0:15:43.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If, by any chance, you're late...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.51,0:15:46.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Killing you will only be\Nthe tip of the iceberg.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.81,0:15:53.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Also, a friend of mine in L.A. has a favorite\NJapanese sweet, so please get some of those, too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.11,0:15:57.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Also, the son of *** in Paris wants\Na figurine from Akihabara...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.28,0:15:59.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with all this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.66,0:16:02.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I got what you asked for!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.45,0:16:05.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Somehow, I made it back in time!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.54,0:16:07.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good job, little boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.25,0:16:09.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kudos to you for making it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.66,0:16:11.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But what a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.25,0:16:13.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're thirty seconds late,\Ndid you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.34,0:16:18.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that you were late\Nby thirty seconds, see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.47,0:16:22.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Means that my schedule will\Nget pushed back thirty seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.09,0:16:25.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A deal that could've been struck\Nif I'd had thirty more seconds
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.10,0:16:27.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,will end up not being\Nstruck, in other words.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.10,0:16:29.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.43,0:16:32.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My motto is, "Time is not money."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.94,0:16:34.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Money can't buy time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.48,0:16:36.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.82,0:16:38.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.65,0:16:40.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you understand\Nthat, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.36,0:16:42.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, what's my next appointment?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.99,0:16:44.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right! Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.62,0:16:46.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A product meeting at AB Corp.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.83,0:16:49.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well! That's\None of my subsidiaries.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.58,0:16:50.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's the building next door.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.87,0:16:52.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, then I'll have them\Nbring the car around.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.58,0:16:54.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That would be wasting\Ntoo much time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.33,0:16:55.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait there for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.79,0:16:58.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's me. I'm coming over there\Nnow, so do your thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.26,0:17:00.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Understood.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.47,0:17:03.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Ms. Hana, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.82,0:17:22.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Hana! Don't tell me you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.58,0:17:39.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We've been waiting for you, Boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.96,0:17:42.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's start this meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.30,0:17:48.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just now, I thought I heard\NRaku's voice from up above.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.14,0:17:56.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But really, look how the whole\Ncity's in full Christmas mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.27,0:17:58.77,DefaultTop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Incoming call
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.27,0:17:59.65,DefaultMid2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Raku
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.15,0:17:58.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,From Raku?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.40,0:17:59.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What does he want?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.77,0:17:59.65,DefaultTop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Connected
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.98,0:18:01.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.32,0:18:03.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}H-Hey... is that you, Chitoge?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.24,0:18:06.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you sound like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.41,0:18:09.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I finally got to go on\Na short break now, see.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.41,0:18:10.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But hey, I have to say...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.83,0:18:13.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Your mom is way\Nbeyond demonic, huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.66,0:18:16.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I get that a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.25,0:18:17.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So, what's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.00,0:18:19.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, nothing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.79,0:18:22.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I just thought you might be feeling down.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.47,0:18:24.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why would I...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.88,0:18:28.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yesterday, what you really\Nwanted was for your mom to say,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.05,0:18:32.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"It makes me so happy to see you\Nstill wearing that ribbon." Right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.73,0:18:35.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It has nothing to do with you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.56,0:18:37.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You know it does. It totally does.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.19,0:18:40.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know how serious Ms. Hana was
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.19,0:18:44.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,about letting us spend the night together\Non Christmas Eve if she approved of me,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.90,0:18:45.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but you...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.99,0:18:49.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What you really want is to spend\NChristmas Eve with your mom, right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.12,0:18:51.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm worried.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.79,0:18:56.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That the truth is my mom doesn't\Nhave the slightest interest in me at all.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.67,0:19:02.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, this is what Mom always\Nasks, every time I see her.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.55,0:19:05.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"How old are you now?"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.47,0:19:07.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She can't seem to remember,\Nno matter how many times I tell her.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.97,0:19:09.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And when I do see her,\Nall she does is yell at me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.68,0:19:11.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She never praises me, not even once.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.60,0:19:16.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And she's always only cold to me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.39,0:19:17.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even this...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.98,0:19:20.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I bet she said that as she doesn't\Nwant to spend Christmas Eve with me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.81,0:19:22.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You know that's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.11,0:19:25.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way she wouldn't\Nwant to see her own daughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.40,0:19:26.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey, don't worry.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.86,0:19:28.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That lady's so swamped,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.78,0:19:32.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but she's always made a point of\Ncoming home for Christmas at least, right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.41,0:19:36.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This time, you invite her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.12,0:19:39.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tell her that you want to\Nspend Christmas Eve with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.75,0:19:44.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you're honest with her about how you feel,\Nshe might come through for you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.30,0:19:46.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You... think so?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.84,0:19:48.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's gonna be all right.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.47,0:19:50.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's your mom, isn't she?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.97,0:19:55.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All right. I'll give it a try.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.47,0:19:57.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Right. Good luck to you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.89,0:20:01.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thank y—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.15,0:20:04.19,DefaultMid2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Raku
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.15,0:20:04.19,DefaultTop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Connected
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.31,0:20:02.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sorry, Chitoge!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.69,0:20:04.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm getting a call from Ms. Hana!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.40,0:20:06.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I gotta get going!\NOkay, give it all you've got!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.15,0:20:09.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.74,0:20:14.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Be honest, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.46,0:20:24.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hello?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.92,0:20:27.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.01,0:20:29.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mother? It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.26,0:20:32.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Chitoge? Well, how unusual.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.30,0:20:33.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Listen...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.76,0:20:35.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What do you want?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.01,0:20:38.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm busy with work right now,\Nso if we could pick this up later...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.14,0:20:40.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry! This won't take long!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.56,0:20:42.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.48,0:20:46.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,about letting Raku and me spend\NChristmas Eve if you approved of him...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.73,0:20:48.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like you to call that off.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.69,0:20:50.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh? But why?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.11,0:20:52.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,M-Mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.28,0:20:55.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I... I'd like to, um, spend it with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.49,0:20:57.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, that's all right.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.04,0:20:59.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't think about me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.16,0:21:02.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You'd rather spend\NChristmas Eve with him, right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.29,0:21:03.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, I...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.75,0:21:07.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And besides, I've switched my schedule\Nto get some work done on Christmas Eve,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.50,0:21:09.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}so either way,\Nit's not going to work.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.17,0:21:12.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is there anything else?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.30,0:21:15.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No? Then I'm hanging up.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.10,0:21:22.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you turn her down?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.81,0:21:24.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.23,0:21:27.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That call just now... it was\Nfrom Chitoge, wasn't it? So why?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.19,0:21:29.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because I have work to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.07,0:21:31.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I wouldn't be\Nspending Christmas Eve with her,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.78,0:21:34.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so I scheduled some\Nappointments beforehand.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.12,0:21:37.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then at least get her\Na Christmas present!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.41,0:21:39.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go out and buy\Nwhatever you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.45,0:21:40.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No need for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.66,0:21:41.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind that,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.71,0:21:45.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I need to get this work done now,\Nsince I have another appointment.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.33,0:21:48.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is your job that important to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.17,0:21:49.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you so into it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.50,0:21:51.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because no one can do it but me,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.01,0:21:55.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and because I'm needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.18,0:22:00.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you have the ability, it's your duty\Nto exercise it... that's my way of thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.06,0:22:04.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As long as I'm needed, I'll\Ncontinue to exercise my abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.60,0:22:09.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, your hands are idle, little boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.23,0:22:11.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Get those documents filed, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.03,0:22:13.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What the hell is that?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.49,0:22:15.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Because no one can do it but me?"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.95,0:22:17.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Because I'm needed?"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.74,0:22:23.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't you see that the person closest\Nto you is the one who needs you the most?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.00,0:22:27.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My bad, Chitoge.{\i0}
